<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Message Delivery Report</title>
  <style>
    /* Reset styles */
    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
      color: #333;
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #ffffff;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
    }
    .logo {
      color: #0284c7;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .content {
      padding: 30px 20px;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }
    .footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #888;
      border-top: 1px solid #eaeaea;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 12px 24px;
      background-color: #0284c7;
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 4px;
      font-weight: bold;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .report-info {
      padding: 20px;
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      border-radius: 4px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .stats {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .stat-box {
      flex: 1;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 0 5px;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .stat-box.total {
      background-color: #e3f2fd;
      border: 1px solid #90caf9;
    }
    .stat-box.delivered {
      background-color: #e8f5e9;
      border: 1px solid #a5d6a7;
    }
    .stat-box.failed {
      background-color: #ffebee;
      border: 1px solid #ef9a9a;
    }
    .stat-number {
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .message-id {
      font-family: monospace;
      word-break: break-all;
      background-color: #f0f0f0;
      padding: 5px;
      border-radius: 3px;
    }
    table {
      width: 100%;
      border-collapse: collapse;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    th, td {
      padding: 12px;
      text-align: left;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea;
    }
    th {
      background-color: #f5f5f5;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <div class="logo">Jay<span style="color: #0369a1;">Link</span> SMS</div>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Message Delivery Report</h2>
      <p>Hello {{firstName}},</p>
      <p>Here's the delivery report for your recent message campaign:</p>

      <div class="report-info">
        <p><strong>Message ID:</strong> <span class="message-id">{{messageId}}</span></p>
        <p><strong>Sent Time:</strong> {{sentTime}}</p>
        
        <div class="stats">
          <div class="stat-box total">
            <div class="stat-number">{{recipients}}</div>
            <div>Total Recipients</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-box delivered">
            <div class="stat-number">{{delivered}}</div>
            <div>Delivered</div>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-box failed">
            <div class="stat-number">{{failed}}</div>
            <div>Failed</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <p>For a detailed breakdown, including delivery status for each recipient, please visit your analytics dashboard:</p>
      <div style="text-align: center;">
        <a href="{{reportUrl}}" class="button">View Full Report</a>
      </div>

      <p>If you have any questions or concerns about this delivery report, please contact our support team.</p>
      <p>Thank you for using JayLink SMS!</p>
      <p>Best regards,<br>The JayLink Team</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{currentYear}} JayLink SMS. All rights reserved.</p>
      {{!-- <p>123 Messaging Street, Communication City</p> --}}
      <p>You received this notification because you have delivery reports enabled in your account settings.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>